{
  "chapter": 257,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕项少龙（化名沈良）在歌舞姬团中的多方周旋展开。张泉被肖月潭设计打伤，项少龙趁机收服张泉，令其依赖自己。董淑贞对项少龙暗生情愫，项少龙承诺帮助她成为继承凤菲的舞姬，换取她的信任与合作。解子元因妻子善柔的转变而欣喜若狂，邀项少龙出游。凤菲与项少龙共进早膳时暧昧互动，最终答应让项少龙安排团内各人的出路，但对韩闯、仲孙龙、吕不韦、田单等权贵的阻碍表示担忧。本章展现了项少龙以柔克刚的策略，通过情感与利益的双重手段拉拢各方势力。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kun_shan",
      "speaker_name": "昆山",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "定是仲孙龙派人干的，临淄真是野蛮人当道的地方，全无法纪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_kun_shan",
      "text": "伤得怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kun_shan",
      "speaker_name": "昆山",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "主要是头、脸中了几拳，眼肿得差点看不到东西，唇角也爆裂，那样子令人看得心中难受。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那些人真狠心，看！打得副管事变成这个样子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是否沈兄来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "你们出去一会儿，我有话和张兄说。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "有什么话是淑贞不能听的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "二小姐请出去片刻。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "究竟是怎么一回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我其实没有什么大碍，他们只是打我的头，又逼问我为何去见主子，我当然死都不肯说。唉！最可恨是主子给我的钱都被抢走，那些钱本是要给你的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "张兄要去见的究竟是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在还不能对你说。唉！想不到有仲孙龙插手在这件事情内，现在我们整团人全在他的爪牙严密监视中，你也要小心点。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "张兄好好休息吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你怎都要帮我这个忙，迟些我再去弄钱回来给你。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "我可为张兄做些什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "设法成为凤菲的心腹，打探她和龙阳君的关系。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "若你是凤菲，就算我成了你的心腹，你会把与自己终身有关的事泄露给我知道吗？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_quan",
      "speaker_name": "张泉",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凤菲是不会相信任何人的，包括龙阳君在内。因为魏王对凤菲亦有野心，所以凤菲最后只能倚赖你，明白吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhang_quan",
      "text": "好吧！我看看怎么办，但一天未收到钱，张兄休想我肯与你合作。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是否在恼人家呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "小人怎敢，二小姐无论怎样骗我和不信任我，我这小管事也只好逆来顺受。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看你怨气冲天的样子，淑贞给你赔罪好吗？唉！人家现在不知该怎样方可讨你欢心，你是否只好男风不爱女色的？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "是否凡认识龙阳君的人，都变成只好男风的呢？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还要瞒人，只看他瞧你的媚样儿，双目喷火似的，便知你是他的男人。因为你若非他的男人，他怎会以这种态度对你。现在淑贞唯一的希望，就是你除了男人外，也欢喜女人。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "那你就当我是你想的那样好了。请问二小姐，可以放我回房休息吗？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你若不欢喜正路，淑贞也可奉陪。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "二小姐的好意，小人心领了。不过你仍未弄清楚一件事，即使你和秀真没与我有亲密关系，我沈良仍会为你们安排好一切，绝不教你们沦为权贵的姬妾。此事若有一字虚言，教我沈良不得好死。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你为何肯这么做？又知否动辄会惹来杀身之祸？若教凤菲知道你要破坏她的计划，第一个不放过你的正是她。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "你说我是傻瓜、笨蛋什么都可以，但我却决定了要这么做，只要你们肯乖乖听话，我便有办法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们还不够乖吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "乖得太过分，不但对我乖，还对张泉和沙立乖，谁有利用价值便对谁乖。但我要求的并不是这种乖，你回去好好想想。但时间已无多，表演过后将是行动的时刻，若错过时机，莫要怪我没有帮你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈良啊！你说得人家六神无主呢！可否清楚点告诉淑贞你为人家做的是何打算呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "你们若再不肯对我推心置腹，恐怕我没有办法帮助你们。我的打算是把你捧为继承凤菲的另一名姬，而凤菲则可安然归隐，过她自己选择的生活。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你说的当然是最理想的安排。但怎办得到呢？凤菲现在视我如敌人，绝不会答应，纵是答应，也须众人都肯承认才行。这根本是不可能的事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "凤菲方面包在我身上，至于你能否成为凤菲以外的另一名姬，就要看你自己的本领。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的本领？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "我会说服凤菲让你在其中一齣歌舞担正主姬的角色，只要你的表演不大逊色，而我又能在例如龙阳君等有身份、有地位的人面前为你美言几句，甚至邀你到某几个权贵处表演，哈！你说那会是怎么样的情况？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你有把握说服凤菲吗？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "给我三天时间，我会教凤菲亲口向你说，你却须和秀真放弃一切不轨行动。现在乖乖地去睡觉吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "董淑贞",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今晚让人家陪你好吗？淑贞给你弄得身子都烫热了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dong_shu_zhen",
      "text": "你不是说我只爱男风吗？去找秀真告诉她这个消息吧！切记不可予第三个人知道，否则就不灵光！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄真行，内子昨晚不但没有怪责我，还准我和你交朋友。她说有你看管我，偶尔出去胡混都没有关系，啊！沈兄真是我的救星和朋友。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "解兄不用上早朝吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "大王昨晚着凉，故休朝一天。嘿！沈兄今晚有空吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "小心尊夫人是试探你的呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我的夫人说得出来的话一定做得到，绝不会是骗我的。她今晚要请沈兄到舍下吃饭，膳后我们可把臂出游，让小弟好好招呼沈兄，哈！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "你好像一刻都等不来的样子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然，只有躺伏在陌生美女的怀里，嗅吸她们的香气，我的脑筋才会灵活起来。唉！你不知大王催得我多么紧，若我写不好柔骨女的贺寿词，今天就真的糟糕。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "你这两天有没有看过兰宫媛的排演？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我怎敢见她，昨天在宫内撞到她的相好齐雨，他还对我冷嘲热讽，若非我脾气好，定要教他好看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄和仲孙龙究竟是什么一回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这就糟了，昨天他派人来试探我和沈兄的关系，我不虞有他，照实说是新相识的朋友，唔！待会儿我要亲自去找他说话，再不然找二王子出头，不信仲孙龙敢不卖账。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "多一事不如少一事，解兄不用插手此事，徒使事情更复杂，我自有应付之法。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄知否仲孙龙在这里的势力可比得上王侯，他若这么吃了沈兄的亏，是绝不会轻易罢手的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "放心吧！若真须解兄帮手，我当然会来求解兄！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "以后有什么事尽管对我说。现在我要赶回官署办事，今晚我来接你好吗？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_guan",
      "speaker_name": "门官",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大小姐到！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "解大人是怎么了？人说过门不入，解大人却是入门都不向凤菲打个招呼！凤菲是如此令大人不屑一顾吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "凤小姐错怪在下，自宫宴见过小姐，在下便给小姐勾去魂魄，直到今天才恢复正常，试问在下还怎敢造次。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "小人护送解大人走好了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "如此尤物，世所罕见。难怪仲孙龙不择手段务要把她弄上手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "解兄心动了？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说来沈兄或不肯相信，每次我回到家中，都会将外边的女人忘得一干二净。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "text": "这就最好，我明白了！解兄只是为了作曲填词才会去青楼胡混的。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jie_zi_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "解子元",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈兄确是我的知己。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "解子元见到你时像换了另一个人般，神情又这么兴奋，究竟他因什么事找你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "这是男人的秘密，大小姐最好不要知道。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你愈来愈不将人家放在眼内，小心我会对你不客气。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐息怒，我们只不过约了今晚到青楼鬼混而已！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "男人是否都是天生的贱骨头，放着这里美女如云，却要付钱去讨好那些庸姿俗色。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐是否暗示连你自己都可任小人一亲香泽呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你还要说这种话！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐莫忘了每次都说自己是被逼的呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "看来是奴家给你勾去魂魄才真。好像你想我开心，凤菲便要开心；要人家苦恼，人家就要苦恼。告诉凤菲好吗？你如今究竟想人家怎样呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "自然是想大小姐乖乖听话，那我就可完成宏愿。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "说吧！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "我希望能依团内每个人的愿望，玉成他们的理想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 335
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我开始相信你确有这种诚意。但问题是你沈良凭什么资格办得到？这不是我答应就成，还牵涉到其他的人与事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "最关键处是大小姐肯否点头，其他的由我解决。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "好吧！算我答应好了。你如何去应付韩闯、仲孙龙、吕不韦和田单这么多有权有势的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 257,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 345
    }
  ],
